{"tid":1943163,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑有人發國難財呃人錢買口罩","createTime":"2020-03-25T13:22:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T15:30:12.000Z","uid":11588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8bf9de4abffc4a40ca248f8971383d5c93b00f91","tid":1943163,"uid":11588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:22:15.000Z","msg":"因為我屋企都無乜口罩<br />\n所以想幫兩老買口罩啦<br />\n本身條友同我講話可以約係青衣交收<br />\n但係佢依家無啦啦轉左順豐話可以今日寄出<br />\n我都唔太信架啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p94RNBa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp94RNBa.png&h=190b3d6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n買左之後過左1日先見到有人講呢樣野<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7WrkFWJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7WrkFWJ.jpg&h=6912e0ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後依家係咁搵佢都無理我<br />\n我都知追討唔到架啦 但如果可以幫手叫佢起身屙夜尿都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c36258be5295bb05ae281b0c7a52a7879b8d10","tid":1943163,"uid":11588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:22:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0195af58b55b13eb728a9bc95e7a3f6b5b549b17","tid":1943163,"uid":11588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:22:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa1c92c3a826987412e08bbd76457d73a7b947ce","tid":1943163,"uid":11588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:29:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"067d69ada471a41b809a13e842ad2c5c62518c68","tid":1943163,"uid":11588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:31:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"260ebc006b2b79014f8212ffd7dc8826e19c9576","tid":1943163,"uid":11588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:36:08.000Z","msg":"推 肯定無人追討架啦 想人幫手打比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa